channel.title: Scar doesnt work for me anymore :(
channel.description:
Ever since I formatted my computer, scar just doesn't work. I have tried just about every script I can find, and I even tried a simple thing where it just finds a color and clicks it(Still didn;t work). However, the problem I am having is that it just doesn't even look for the color. It just sits there and lags really bad.
I have silent mouse turned off. I have used the crosshair on the runescape client And I know I've set everything up properly, I have set my own colors, I've literally tried everything I can.
Anyone have any ideas/suggestions? Thanks
